  ('Bryan Cleary', 'Founder - eCommerce Growth Consultant & CRO Specialist', 'Founder | eCommerce Growth Consultant | Shopify/Shopify Plus expert | Ecommerce Coach at BOOM · Ecommerce growth consultant with over 14 years of experience in digital product, project and account management while working across scoping, UX/Design, web development, branding and digital marketing I have become an expert in ensuring that clients achieve their goals. I have worked with a diverse range of clients from the E-Commerce, NFP, Education and Pharmaceutical sectors helping each to transform their organisations through technology.I now focus on 1 to 1 e-commerce consulting taking a ho', 'Greater Sydney Area', '14+ years operating experience in ANZ and international markets.', ARRAY['International Founder', 'Sales / GTM'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/bryan-cleary-2080208a', NULL, NULL, 'Va-va Voom Digital', FALSE, '[{"name": "Va-va Voom Digital"}, {"name": "Boom - Aussie Ecommerce Training"}]'::jsonb, 'ireland', ARRAY['ireland', 'australia'], NULL, 'bryan-cleary', 'International Founder', ARRAY['both'], TRUE, FALSE),
