  ('Stevie-Ann Dovico', 'Group Executive Technology', 'Group Executive Technology | CIO50 2024 & 2025 | IT News Financial Services Technology Leader of the Year 2025 | Executive Leader of the Year 2022 Women in Digital | GAICD · Stevie is a dynamic and visionary Business and Technology leader with 20 years of experience in Banking, Financial Services, Telecommunications and Consulting. She has proven experience as a Group Executive, Chief Information Officer (CIO), Board Director, Advisory Board and Committee Member and as an Executive General Manager of Technology for some of Australia’s largest organisations. Stevie has successfully led large, cross functional, global teams of over 600 employees, across Technology, Di', 'Sydney, New South Wales, Australia', '20+ years operating experience in ANZ and international markets.', ARRAY['Scaled Founder', 'Financial Services', 'Recognised Industry Leader'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/stevieanndovico', NULL, NULL, 'Beyond Bank Australia', FALSE, '[{"name": "Beyond Bank Australia"}, {"name": "NAB"}]'::jsonb, 'uk', ARRAY['uk', 'australia'], NULL, 'stevie-ann-dovico', 'Scaled Founder', ARRAY['both'], TRUE, FALSE),
