  ('Colm Dolan', 'Chief Executive Officer', 'Entrepreneur | Advisor | Investor · Experience• Founder & CEO of Publift (10 years)• Scaled a technology business from zero to $20m ARR• Built and led global teams across Australia, Ireland, and the Philippines• Delivered sustained ~40% YoY growth with strong profitability• Successfully exited and supported the business post-acquisition⸻Key Skills• Scaling businesses and simplifying complexity• Building high-performance teams and future leaders• Creating strong, values-led cultures• Driving disciplined growth with real profit• Lea', 'Greater Sydney Area', 'Senior operator with extensive ANZ market experience.', ARRAY['Scaled Founder', 'Fundraising / Investment'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/colm-dolan', NULL, NULL, 'Dolo Ventures', FALSE, '[{"name": "Dolo Ventures"}, {"name": "Publift"}]'::jsonb, 'ireland', ARRAY['ireland', 'australia'], NULL, 'colm-dolan', 'Scaled Founder', ARRAY['both'], TRUE, FALSE),
  ('James Bergl', 'Co-Founder & Managing Partner Bluebird APAC', 'Ex-SaaS Operators | 100+ SaaS Sales Hires | Helping SaaS Leaders Recruit Australia’s Top 1% AEs & Sales Leaders · Most SaaS leaders don’t struggle to “hire”.They struggle to find the people who can actually sell.After 17 years building and leading high-performing SaaS and MSP sales teams (Datto, Pax8, N-able), I realised something:The best AEs, SDRs, and Sales Leaders in Australia are almost never applying to job ads. They’re too busy performing.That’s where we come in.At Bluebird, we’re ex-operators turned talent partners, helping SaaS leaders recruit Australia’s top 1 percent - the people who ramp fast, c', 'Greater Sydney Area', '17+ years operating experience in ANZ and international markets.', ARRAY['Active Advisor', 'Fundraising / Investment'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/jbergl', NULL, NULL, 'Bluebird', FALSE, '[{"name": "Bluebird"}, {"name": "Pavilion"}]'::jsonb, 'uk', ARRAY['uk', 'australia'], NULL, 'james-bergl', 'Active Advisor', ARRAY['international_entrant'], TRUE, FALSE),
