  ('Nigel Williams', 'Strategic Advisor', 'Non-Executive Director, recently retired as Commonwealth Bank Chief Risk Officer. Director ASB Bank, Director Cancer Council NSW & Chair Audit, Risk & Technology Committee. MAICD · I joined Commonwealth Bank in 2018 as Group Chief Risk Officer after the APRA Prudential Review to improve the Group’s Risk Management, Culture and Governance. It has been great being part of the leadership team that has made CBA the success it is today delivering industry leading Total Shareholder Return in this period.I have had 20+ years experience in both C-Suite roles and on Boards. The Board roles have been across Australia, NZ, China and Switzerland. This includes three different banks, e', 'Sydney, New South Wales, Australia', '20+ years operating experience in ANZ and international markets.', ARRAY['Active Advisor', 'Compliance / Risk', 'Recognised Industry Leader'], 'https://linkedin.com/in/williams-nigel', NULL, NULL, 'Clayton Utz', FALSE, '[{"name": "Clayton Utz"}, {"name": "ASB Bank"}]'::jsonb, 'usa', ARRAY['usa', 'australia'], NULL, 'nigel-williams', 'Active Advisor', ARRAY['both'], TRUE, FALSE),
